    "body": "Remappings seem to be popular and usable. The effects of `=/something` might be unexpected though, and certainly do not provide a fallback feature as suggested in the documentation (perhaps it would even be a security problem if they did).\r\n\r\nBecause of that I would propose to disallow an empty remapping source starting from 0.5.0.",
